<section .hero.is-primary.is-medium>
    <div .hero-body.container>
        <div .columns>
            <div .column.is-4>
                <img .is-hidden-mobile src="@{StaticR imgs_stack_png}">
            <div .column.has-text-centered>
                <h1 .title>Yesodâ€”notes
                <p .subtitle>Blazing fast note-taking
                <p .content>
                    <strong>Write, read and share some notes.
                $maybe _ <- muid
                    <a .button.is-light.is-large href=@{NotesR}>
                        <span .icon>
                            <i .fas.fa-sticky-note>
                        <span>Your Notes
                $nothing
                    <a .button.is-light.is-large href=@{AuthR LoginR}>
                        <span .icon>
                            <i .fas.fa-sign-in-alt>
                        <span>Login

<section #hero-tabs .hero.is-primary>
    <div .hero-foot>
        <nav .tabs.is-boxed.is-centered>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <a href="#bulma">Bulma
                <li>
                    <a href="#javascript">JavaScript
                <li>
                    <a href="#json">Json API
                <li>
                    <a href="#cookies">Cookies
                <li>
                    <a href="#about">About

<section #bulma .hero.is-medium.is-light>
    <div .hero-body.container>
        <div .columns>
            <div .column>
                <img src="https://bulma.io/images/made-with-bulma--semiblack.png">
            <div .column.has-text-centered>
                <h1 .title.is-hidden-mobile>Bulma CSS Framework
                <p .subtitle>A modern open source CSS framework based on Flexbox
                <a .button.is-info href="https://bulma.io/">Check it out

<section #javascript .hero.is-warning.is-bold>
    <div .hero-body.container>
        <div .columns>
            <div .column.has-text-centered.content>
                <h1>A little bit of Javascript...
                <p>Some Jquery and Ajax code is used for in-page interactions
                <h1>... or none at all.
                <p>you can disable javascript in your browser and this website will still work perfectly
            <div .column.is-3>
                <img .is-hidden-mobile src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6a/JavaScript-logo.png">

<section #json .hero.is-light>
    <div .hero-body.container>
        <div .columns>
            <div .column.is-3>
                <img src="https://www.vectorlogo.zone/logos/json/json-card.png">
            <div .column.has-text-centered>
                <h1 .title.is-hidden-mobile>JSON API
                <p .subtitle>You can POST and GET using json on most pages, just use <code>application/json</code> as your HTTP Accept Header

<section #cookies .hero.is-info.is-bold>
    <div .hero-body.container>
        <div .has-text-centered>
            <h1 .title>Cookies
            <p .subtitle>We use just one, necessary, cookie
            <a .button.is-success href=@{CookiesR}>Read More

<section #about .hero.is-medium.is-light>
    <div .hero-body.container>
        <div .has-text-centered.content>
            <h1>About
            <p>This website is a toy project that I made to get familiar with the Yesod Web Framework
            <p>It's open source. If you'd like to know more, make a suggestion or open up an issue:
            <a .button.is-dark href="https://github.com/pasqu4le/yesod-notes">
                <span .icon>
                    <i .fab.fa-github-alt>
                <span>Github Page

